49:28.566 --> 49:32.034
        So, the werewolf
 falls in love with the bride.

49:32.036 --> 49:34.470
     What would he do next?

49:34.472 --> 49:38.174
 Would he maybe eat something?

49:38.176 --> 49:40.209
   No, that's not what people
    do when they re in love.

49:40.211 --> 49:42.611
 They recite poetry and stuff.

49:42.613 --> 49:44.413
         But you re not
      ready to do that yet

49:44.415 --> 49:46.082
  because you have a problem:

