          Don't worry!
   The wedding's in two days.

01:11:16.473 --> 01:11:21.342
   I won't let a thing happen
 to these two beautiful girls.

01:11:21.344 --> 01:11:22.577
         Are you ready
        for the big day?

01:11:22.579 --> 01:11:23.678
              Yup!

01:11:23.679 --> 01:11:24.778
          I've got my
     ordination certificate

01:11:24.781 --> 01:11:27.382
       from the Universal
    Life Church. right here.

01:11:27.384 --> 01:11:29.651
    Am I the only one who's
  noticed that they've chosen

01:11:29.653 --> 01:11:32.720
       a self-proclaimed
      witch to marry them?

01:11:32.722 --> 01:11:35.857
Okay, I think that's everything!

01:11:35.859 --> 01:11:38.760
        You won't forget
    that the ice sculptures

01:11:38.762 --> 01:11:40.028
      arrive Friday night

01:11:40.030 --> 01:11:41.996
          and the dove
     wrangler will be here

01:11:41.998 --> 01:11:44.399
        bright and early
       Saturday morning.

01:11:44.401 --> 01:11:45.800
         Yeah, got it.

01:11:45.802 --> 01:11:46.934
             Okay!

01:11:46.936 --> 01:11:48.353
           Well boys

01:11:48.354 --> 01:11:49.771
         why don't you
    drive us to the airport

01:11:49.773 --> 01:11:54.008
     and then you can pick
   up the fireworks displays?

01:12:08.992 --> 01:12:11.426
  Thank God it's nearly over.

01:12:11.428 --> 01:12:13.695
             OSCAR
            You know

01:12:13.696 --> 01:12:15.963
  I never thought Zilla would
  be the type to want a crazy

01:12:15.965 --> 01:12:18.032
  elaborate wedding like this.

01:12:18.034 --> 01:12:21.102
       Oh, Zilla doesn't
       want this wedding.

01:12:27.010 --> 01:12:29.844
       (SOFT JAZZ PLAYS)

01:12:38.755 --> 01:12:40.655
We could still win the contest.

01:12:40.657 --> 01:12:42.357
          We have some
       really good stuff.

