       (CREAKING SOUNDS)

01:20:11.874 --> 01:20:13.541
      This will be great.

01:20:13.543 --> 01:20:15.943
         Are you sure?

01:20:15.945 --> 01:20:18.095
           Of course.

01:20:18.096 --> 01:20:20.246
      The werewolf will be
 silhouetted against the trees.

