         No, I mean are
      you sure it's safe?

01:20:23.886 --> 01:20:26.220
         Stunt doubles
      do it all the time.

01:20:26.222 --> 01:20:29.056
       Well yeah, but I'm
 pretty sure a lot of them die.

01:20:29.058 --> 01:20:31.075
            If I die

