   You did this to yourself.

01:20:38.434 --> 01:20:40.201
  I didn't do this to myself!

01:20:40.203 --> 01:20:41.335
        Your mother did.

01:20:41.337 --> 01:20:43.070
            Exactly.
        And you let her.

01:20:43.072 --> 01:20:45.873
   What part of my childhood
 stories do you not understand?

01:20:45.875 --> 01:20:48.142
     Do not let this woman
  get within three feet of you

01:20:48.144 --> 01:20:50.511
    with mascara, a curling
