01:20:50.513 --> 01:20:52.580
      I wouldn't have had
     to if you hadn't left!

01:20:52.582 --> 01:20:54.582
        Oh, I'm supposed
       to sit around here

01:20:54.584 --> 01:20:56.917
      and let my head get
dipped into toxic waste because

01:20:56.919 --> 01:20:59.086
   you don't have the guts to
