01:21:44.367 --> 01:21:47.434
       Just focus on the
     cinematography, okay?

01:21:52.375 --> 01:21:56.510
   I didn't want to tell you
 this until after the wedding.

01:21:56.512 --> 01:22:00.014
    Your father and I just..

01:22:00.016 --> 01:22:04.184
             well,
